product_info.long_description: With the latest Ball? technology, the Dyson DC50 Multifloor turns on the spot and is easy to steer close to edges and into awkward spaces. Lightweight and durable, it weighs only 5.4kg and features an advanced cleaner head that's engineered for increased dirt pick-up across all floors. It adjusts automatically to all floor types and its brush bar contains carbon fibre filaments for removing fine dust from hard floors.    Emptying the bin on a Dyson vacuum is quick and hygienic; simply press the button to release the dirt. The bin is clear so you can see when it needs emptying, as well as view the amount of dust, dirt and pet hair that the powerful Dyson DC50 Multifloor has captured.
